high_descs: Turn left, head to sink, turn left, head to tub.
Pick up the dirty rag in the tub.
Turn around, move to the sink on the left.
Wash the dirty rag in the sink with water.
Bring the cleaned rag to the tub on the left.
Put the cleaned rag in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned rag in the tub.

high_descs: Turn around and cross the room to face the bath tub.
Pick up the dirty rag in the bath tub.
Turn to the right and face the left side sink.
Wash the rag in the sink and pick it back up.
Turn around and walk forward to the bath tub.
Place the clean rag in the front of the tub by the drain.
anns.task_desc: To clean a rag as well as put it back in the bath tub.

high_descs: Knock the empty toilet paper tube over, then turn left to face the opposite direction and go to the bathtub.
Pick up the washcloth from the tub.
Turn right and go to the nearest sink.
Rinse the washcloth in the left sink.
Turn left and return to the tub.
Toss the washcloth back into the tub.
anns.task_desc: Throw a rinsed washcloth back into the bathtub it came from.
